author: @Achan123-v9y
text:
Hey boy Look, I’m gonna make this simple for you you got two choices YES or YES? Ah 
どぅる ちゅんえ はなまん こるら
둘 중에 하나만 골라
ふたつの中からひとつだけ選んで YES or YES?
Ah ah 
はなまん そんてけ おそ
하나만 선택해 어서 
ひとつだけ選んで 早く
YES or YES? ねが いろっけど いぎちょぎよっとんが 내가 이렇게도 이기적이었던가
私ってこんなにも自分勝手だったかな
 むぉんが いろっけ かっこ しぷとん ちょぎそんな 뭔가 이렇게 갖고 싶던 적 있었나 
こんなに何かを手に入れたかったことがあったかな
 た のるら ね っぽんっぽんはめ 다 놀라 내 뻔뻔함에
みんな驚く 私の図々しさに
 Come on and tell me yes
 
せんがっぼだ くぁかめじん なえ しなりお 생각보다 과감해진 나의 시나리오
思ったより大胆になった私のシナリオ
 い ちょんど ぷれにみょん わんびょけ まんじょけ 이 정도 Plan이면 완벽해 만족해
このくらいのPlanなら完璧ね 満足よ
I don’t care 
 ぬが むぉれど
누가 뭐래도
誰がなんて言ったって
You better tell me yes 
ね まむん ちょんへっそ 내 맘은 정했어 
私の心は決まった
 
YES!
 くろむ いじぇ に てだぷる とぅる ちゃれ 그럼 이제 네 대답을 들을 차례
じゃあ次はあなたの返事を聞く番ね
 
ひんどぅるみょん ぼぎる じゅるけ のん こるぎまね 힘들면 보기를 줄게 넌 고르기만 해 
難しいなら選択肢をあげるわ あなたはただ選べばいい
 
こみなる ぴりょど おぷけ へじゅるけ 고민할 필요도 없게 해줄게
悩む必要さえなくしてあげるから  むぉる こるじ もるら じゅんびへぶぁっそ 뭘 고를지 몰라 준비해봤어
何を選ぶかわからなくて準備したの
 
とぅる ちゅんえ はなまん こるら 둘 중에 하나만 골라
ふたつの中からひとつだけ選んで
 YES or YES?
 
に まうむる もるら じゅんびへぶぁっそ 네 마음을 몰라 준비해봤어
あなたの気持ちがわからなくて準備したの
 
はなまん そんてけ おそ 하나만 선택해 어서
ひとつだけ選んで 早く
 YES or YES?  しろぬん しろ な あにみょん うり 싫어는 싫어 나 아니면 우리?
イヤはイヤよ 私じゃなきゃ私たち？
 
そんてぐる ちょんじゅんへ こじょるん こじょれ 선택을 존중해 거절은 거절해
選択を尊重するわ 拒絶はお断り
 
そんてくちぬん はな ちゃ そんてぐん に まむ 선택지는 하나 자 선택은 네 맘
選択肢はひとつ さあ 選択はお好きなように
 It’s all up to you

author: @ohasia3766
text:
Ahh, TWICE never disappoints. Every year, I'm more impressed. These girls have such great talent that they need to be recognized by the world.

Momo is a great dancer, I really love her charisma.💙
Sana is very cute and her Japanese accent always adds a special touch to the music.💘
Dahyun is the '' sun '' of the group, always bringing joy to the members.🧡
Chaeyoung is a rapper who deserves much recognition by JYP, and her few lines should be appreciated.💜
Tzuyu is simply amazing in dance, in the voice, in everything basically, besides being super tender.💞
Mina is the person that all members love, for their love of music, their effort to always try to be better, she deserves a lot of admiration.❣💚
Jeongyeon even though he does not have many lines in the songs, his voice is charming, his dance is contagious and his cuteness is always our refuge.💖
Nayeon is simply a little princess, who never disappoints us and is always willing to improve, I love this girl.💗
And finally, our leader Jihyo, who strives for the songs, the dances, and not only for this. She is always smiling, always makes the girls laugh. Always tries to please the fans. This girl is a person's love.💕

*TWICE DESERVES RECOGNITION AND LOTS OF LOVE!* ❤

author: @Satopi3104
text:
twice is upping the ante with their dancing!  first dance the night away and now this. technical harder, more complicated formations and more aerobically challenging. You can see the weaker dancers kinda struggling with this (the way they did with dtna lol) but glad to see them not resting on their "successor to GG" laurels but trying to show growth.  Twice in general still have a lot to improve in terms of technique (the lack of sync in their arm movements especially annoy me as well as the sloppiness of the technically difficult moves in the pre-chorus (the clap/shoulder/chest isolation move and the crab leg move) and they are no gfriend, but since they're not marketed as a dance heavy group like gfriend are and their fans and the public probably don't scrutinize their dance that much this level is surely meeting expectations.  they can impress less discerning fans than people like me (and I don't mean that in a mean way or condescending way, but dancers will look at this differently than non-dancers, simple as that) with dances that even to the untrained eye look much harder than their earlier stuff but they still make sure that the signature move is super simple and can be learned in an instant (the whole chicken dance - point finger thing in the deul chung e hana man keolla (and no, that is not the correct romanization of hangeul, i know) part), so that it can easily be copied and reproduced, which is what matters for creating "buzz".  They are aiming for best of both worlds and yes, they should keep improving their technique and range, but I overall agree with the approach.  Interesting also that as the dances get harder it allows you to really tell who is actually a really good dancer and not just competent - jihyo stands out just because she is marketed as a vocal but those 10 years of training don't lie. She dances with the most confidence along with momo and mina (no surprise there).   This year twice have been really busy so in the limited amount of time they've had to learn all of the dances they released this year, the difference in skill and experience become a hell of a lot more pronounced. 

minor point but the sound of momo and/or sana's knee(s) hitting the ground at 1:56 makes me cringe every time. I know why she/they is/are going down so hard (to actually stay on the beat and not cheat and ease into it like the others) but owwww, be careful!

author: @nabila5971
text:
I love the dance but it's just unsynchronised, especially the "roll"ing part before the chorus (in this video 1:02-1:08), they're terrible, especially Nayeon (and I LOVE Nayeon). I know this dance is probably quite hard to do, but they did such a good job with dance the night away..

Mina: slacking with the details
Nayeon: ALWAYS 1 beat behind the others, and it's so obvious.. She's the one making the dance look "messy" the most, since her position is in the front
Sana: great, deserve to be the center of the part, maybe it's because she practices more than the others since it's her part
Tzuyu: ALWAYS 1 beat early, not as obvious as Nayeon
Chae: slacking with the details
Jihyo: 1 beat early and it's pretty obvious
Jeongyeon: 1 beat off and it's like she is always suddenly blank and doesn't know what to do in the middle, messy details, as if she hasn't got the hang of it yet, and she's usually a good dancer and her moves were always easy on the eyes
Momo: perfect, like every single movement she does HAS A PURPOSE because she executes the movements with EFFORT to hit the DETAILS perfectly, she got really awesome sense of rhythm
Dahyun: not even bothering to do the "roll", really flat

I think it's NOT THEIR FAULT tho... I hope the choreographer might consider to give moves that suit their skills better next time. Like this is too many details in such limited time. Hard to execute, especially with NINE members. It's super hard to synchronise people that many, and with different level of dancing ability.

And ONCE AGAIN: I LOVE NAYEON AND ALL THE GIRLS, I love twice, I love the dance, just NOT THAT PART.

author: @Sese.m6358
text:
Well well for the new Onces let me help you , I'm a Once since LOA's era so It might help you :

Beige Tee shirt : Im Nayeon : (1995)The Oldest (known as the Fake Maknae bc of her aegyo) , The Face of the Group, the lead vocalist and dancer . She is Korean too.💘💗

Dark Red jumpsuit: Yoo Jeongyeon (1996) : The lead vocal , dancer , has some acting skills and Gong Seungyeon's (the actress) sister. Korean too.💟💜

Turquoise Blue pants : Hirai Momo (1996) , the Main Dancer, vocal and rapper. She is one of the Japanese Line (along with Sana and Mina) and Heechul's favorite. ( for the newbi : Heechul : member of Super Junior and one of the Knowing Brother's host).💘

White shirt and Black pants : Minatozaki Sana (aka no Sana no life ) (1996) : She is known as the cutie-sexy of the group , Shy Shy Shy girl , vocal , lead dancer and she's from the Japanese line. 💖💋

Crop top and pants black : Park Jihyo (my bias ❤) (born in 1997) : She was trained for 10years so she is known by many others JYP artists ( she trained with Wonder Girls , Miss A etc..), Leader , Main Vocal of the group and Dancer She's Korean.❣❤

Black top and Beige pants : Myoui Mina (1997) :(known as the Black Swan because she did ballet and she's so damn elegant )  She's Japanese but was born in Texas (USA), She is also one of the Visual line (along with Nayeon and Tzuyu) ,Lead Dancer and Lead vocalist. 💓💜

Purple Hair : Kim Dahyun ( 1998 )  :  known as the extra queen of the group. We called her "Dubu" which means "Tofu" bc her skin is as smooth as tofu  , she is the lead rapper , dancer and she is korean😻💙

Dark Green ( black?) Jumpsuit : the cute smol of the group : Son Chaeyoung : (1999) : She is one of the maknae of the group and the Main Rapper (she' also had a good vocal tho ) . She is also known as the Strawberry Princess and she's korean🍓💞

White top and Red pants : Chou Tzuyu : (1999) :Maknae of the group , Taiwanese , She is also the Visual of the group , lead dancer ,vocalist and she is also known as the  Yoda of the group 😂 so adorable ,her fellow members love her so much.💜 💕

WELL They all love each other and also love their Onces , they're so damn adorable and are hard-workers ,they were bashed since their debut so i'm more than joyful that people recognize their talents and stan these 9 angels ❣❣❣❣

I think mina has the most technical training with ballet and contemporary, but she doesn't do very well with twice's style of dance and it doesn't really showcase how great of a dancer she actually is. It also seems like she's tired or lacking energy...and I think that may be because she injured her ankle recently? I don't know tbh.

For the new ONCE ♥︎

Wearing: White bottoms and Black/Pink shirt (brown hair) ♡

🍫🦅 Dahyun: Center at 1:53 - 2:00
Wearing: all black (hair is blonde with purple tips) ♡

🐯🍓 Chaeyoung: .. Baby cub is never center... ( she’s the one lip-syncing at 1:58 - 2:01 )

🐶😎 Tzuyu: Center at 0:19 - 0:24 
Wearing: White top and Red bottoms
(Tallest member) ♡


Hope this helped! And if you’re wondering why I put them in this order, it’s because it’s from oldest to youngest.

author: @yenkoyeniko5180
text:
After DTNA, I guess this must be easier for them but still this is one of the toughest dance for them (DTNA and Signal also). From what I'd observed, they started using their leg movement more often in 2018 compared to the other songs for last 2 years which is a prove that they had improved so much. They become more sychronize with more powerful movement. 
This is just my opinion, Tzuyu'd improved so much since trainee. She'd improved the most in singing and dancing as well. Others were also improved a lot too but I found Tzuyu'd improved the most. 

DTNA is still the best choreo and became my fav choreograph despite a lot of people not favor DTNA as much as their other songs. Yes or yes is great and I'm not regret to stan TWICE.
